  <div class="card-body">
    <h5 class="card-title">I want to adopt a Rabbit</h5>
    <p class="card-text">While some rabbits are gregarious, others may be shy and try to hide when they are first adopted. Therefore, it’s critical that new owners spend time petting and handling their new bunnies to help them transition happily into their new environment.</p>
